room_title: Escape room "1920’s Speakeasy Murder Mystery" by Escape USA in Atlanta
room_description: You’re a local detective in a bar frequented by mobsters, thieves, and murderers, looking for the one who killed the bar owner. You got a tip for the bar owners wife saying that clues are hidden in the bar leading to who killed her husband. You have to figure out who and why soon and escape with the proof before the mafia returns to cover up all of the evidence…
